<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
                
<p n="1">Prosperity! Fortune!</p>
<p n="2-4">Year twenty-seven of the victorious king Nandivikramavarman.</p>
<p n="4-7">Ceruvaliyār, son of Nāyakar Ataṭṭiyār, who fell in a cattle-raid at Curaikkuḷam in the Palkuṉrākkōṭṭam 
<supplied reason="explanation">and</supplied> in the Maṇṭaikuḷanāṭu, obtained a land.</p>

         </div>
         

         
